<i>♪ To be loving you ♪</i>

18:03.879 --> 18:05.402
<i> Oh, hi. </i>

18:05.489 --> 18:07.706
Ted! What is this?

18:07.794 --> 18:09.320
<i>Well, I couldn't let
our anniversary go</i>

18:09.408 --> 18:10.473
<i>without a celebration.</i>

18:10.561 --> 18:11.926
<i>Just because we're not in
the same city</i>

18:12.018 --> 18:13.630
<i>doesn't mean that we can't go
on a date.</i>

18:13.718 --> 18:15.128
And you're wearing
the little tie

18:15.216 --> 18:17.761
with your short-sleeved shirt.
My little Galapo-guy.

18:17.849 --> 18:19.973
<i>Yeah, it's actually really
hot here,</i>

18:20.061 --> 18:22.580
<i>so the bottom half is just my
bathing suit and flip-flops.</i>

18:22.668 --> 18:25.683
Ted! More about your
bottom half, please!

18:25.778 --> 18:28.347
<i>Twyla's not standing right
behind you, is she?</i>

18:29.165 --> 18:30.636
Hi, Ted.

18:30.866 --> 18:32.258
<i>Twyla, again,</i>

18:32.346 --> 18:33.894
<i>I can't thank you enough
for making this happen.</i>

18:34.060 --> 18:36.520
Um, I can lock up
if you wanna go, Twy.

18:36.607 --> 18:38.261
Oh, someone has to serve you
dinner.

18:38.348 --> 18:41.368
But don't worry,
I'll stay out of your way.

18:43.104 --> 18:46.530
<i>Alexis, I'm sorry for
dropping the ball on our calls.</i>

18:46.617 --> 18:48.662
<i>I thought that we would have
Wi-Fi on the trip</i>

18:48.749 --> 18:50.698
<i>and we didn't, so...
the rest of the team</i>

18:50.786 --> 18:52.623
<i>just had to listen to me talk
about you for seven days.</i>

18:52.710 --> 18:56.329
In fact, they actually named
the new fly "Alexis."

18:56.448 --> 18:58.339
The fly that mates
with itself?

18:58.960 --> 19:01.457
<i>Yeah, I think the important
thing is that, now,</i>

19:01.545 --> 19:03.808
<i>I have a little Alexis here
with me,</i>

19:03.981 --> 19:05.419
<i>just buzzing around.</i>

19:05.685 --> 19:08.596
I'm just like so happy
to see your face.

19:08.710 --> 19:10.130
Me too.

19:10.946 --> 19:13.122
- <i>♪ So lucky ♪</i>
- Boop!

19:13.209 --> 19:14.732
- Boop!
- <i>♪ To be loving you ♪</i>

19:25.452 --> 19:27.657
Okay, John, I'm going to
throw another name at you:

19:27.745 --> 19:29.965
Ronnie. Owns her own business,
no kids.

19:30.052 --> 19:32.663
Clearly doesn't spend any money
on herself.

19:32.750 --> 19:35.840
I appreciate the enthusiasm,
Moira, but uh...

19:35.927 --> 19:38.538
I just got off the phone
with Betty Terkstra.

19:38.884 --> 19:40.434
She sold the place.

19:41.275 --> 19:42.451
No, John!

19:42.539 --> 19:45.239
I'll keep an eye open
for a less pricey property,

19:45.327 --> 19:46.694
but, uh, without Stevie,

19:46.782 --> 19:48.330
I think we're in a bit
of a bind.

19:48.418 --> 19:50.777
Oh, John, hold me.

19:51.076 --> 19:53.320
Good is coming, it has to.

19:59.947 --> 20:01.561
Hello, Johnny!

20:01.648 --> 20:03.586
Look, I appreciate
the gesture, guys,

20:03.674 --> 20:06.068
but, uh, this is not a good
night for champagne.

20:06.262 --> 20:08.046
Oh, speak for yourself, John.

20:08.133 --> 20:11.491
Oh good, you're lying down!
We have big news.

20:11.579 --> 20:14.626
If you're referring to the
bath-time video Gwen posted...

20:14.714 --> 20:16.934
N-no, n-no, it's...
it's not that exciting.

20:17.022 --> 20:18.937
No, um...

20:19.025 --> 20:21.571
Well, we...

20:22.882 --> 20:25.623
- BOUGHT THE MOTEL!
- What?!

20:25.718 --> 20:28.544
Yeah, we took out a second
mortgage on our house.

20:28.632 --> 20:31.546
Yeah. After what went down
at dinner,

20:31.634 --> 20:33.278
Joc and I started talking,
and we figured,

20:33.366 --> 20:36.242
well, if it's good enough
for Bill Gates to invest in,

20:36.330 --> 20:38.555
it's, uh, good enough for us
to invest in.

20:38.642 --> 20:40.383
Roland, we don't actually
know...

20:40.470 --> 20:43.646
I'm, I'm sorry,
I'm, I'm not comprehending.

20:43.765 --> 20:45.506
We...

20:45.608 --> 20:48.039
are buying into the business.

20:48.703 --> 20:51.504
Say hello to your new
business partners.

20:51.773 --> 20:54.951
Oh, well, if that's not cause
for alcohol

20:55.039 --> 20:56.485
I don't know what is.

20:56.573 --> 20:58.618
So, we have the motel?

20:58.705 --> 20:59.973
We sure do.

21:00.061 --> 21:02.411
Now, first order of business,

21:02.646 --> 21:04.257
we need name tags.

21:06.601 --> 21:09.856
I don't believe this!
Roland, we will make this work.

21:09.944 --> 21:11.063
- Yes.
- We'll make it work.

21:11.151 --> 21:13.804
- Thank you. Thank you, Roland.
- All right.

21:16.616 --> 21:18.485
Why is there a turtle
on the floor?

21:18.727 --> 21:20.294
Alexis!

